lines.text: There are three brands of brothers-in-law - The "Gimmies," the "Let Me Haves", and, the "Do Me A Favor" kind.

[Harold wakes the baby]
Nine rooms in the house and you have to come HERE to sneeze.
If I had to break something why couldn't it have been a leg?

[Harold trips on a wagon and falls downstairs]
If you must play why don't you go to the den?
I'm the night watchman, what's all this racket about?
